snippet.textDisplay:
It's time to wake up! it's time that we go back to God.
this is a testimony of ex devil worshipper John Ramirez
https://youtu.be/I11L71PD3Lw

These things are real. God is going to judge us. The Kingdom of Heaven is at hand.
Who will stand before God holy? No one can stand righteous in front of Him with our own works.
We have evil inside us pure evil! jealousy, hatred, anger, adultery, lust, etc
But God sent His Son Jesus to die for us, to pay THAT price of our sins
If we repent and believe Him, He will come into us and live in us and He will transform us.
I was clubbing every week, never believed in God and was addicted to sooo many things.
Then I wanted to die because I thought life was meaningless. But I sought God. And I came under His presence three years ago. Jesus Christ is the Lord and Savior. He is the King of kings that people don't know.
This world today is in great darkness, so many people are deceived thinking even that there is no God, just like me.
But He is so real even real than us. It's more than a spirit.
This is a being that has the authority to send us to hell and heaven.
Instant moment, I knew I was going to hell. But God showed me love, an eternal love I have never known in my life ever.
You know God loves you so much? That's why He sent His Son Jesus to die for you.
Jesus loves you so so much. So so so much that He cries over your soul. It's so sweet to have a relationship with Jesus who is the King of this universe.
After that, I gave my life surrendered to Jesus and as the Bible promises, His Spirit came over me and transformed me.
Humans don't change but when you surrender your life to Jesus, Spirit of God will come upon you and He will change you.
All my addictions disappeared in one day supernaturally. It is a true story.
Come to Jesus before it's too late! America is going to enter a hard time.
Prophecies in the Bible are being fulfilled. It's time to wake up and pray.
